attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a rolling cart. He starts by unbolting all four wheels. Later rotate the furniture and continue to remove the hexagon cap nut, screw and brackets to disassemble the first tray, continue with the second tray, and with the third tray, to be able to disassemble the side bars using the screwdriver and to finish disassembling the base frame.
